{
  "texts": [
    "This study examines the role of generative AI in the future of software development and proposes primary future scenarios S1-4, as frameworks for understanding its role and potential.",
    "Using these scenarios, we analyzed potential advancements, shift(s), trajectories and also risks for different SDO cases from the industry: legacy, clean slate, networked, and special operations.",
    "We also addressed critical challenges and ethical considerations.",
    "Generative AI presents promising prospects in multiple levels of SDOs and offers a strategic tool to drive productivity, resource optimization, and cost/time savings.",
    "Since the introduction of GPT3 and 4 the adoption speed of the software development community has been phenomenal."
  ]
}